  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121620/extras/70946f58e8a2006256bea87e41f16387.avif?t=1736109859\" width=616 height=616 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What will come?:</strong> We will release minor updates to fix issues and minor implementations, and major updates adding content and mechanics mentioned in the RoadMap.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Paid Content or Microtransactions?: </strong>Our vision for The King Cat Clicker is to be an IDLE/Clicker where you only pay for the game and receive future content without the need for additional expenses, we are committed to creating a game without ADs, microtransactions, inventory items or any predatory mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will the game become more expensive?:</strong> The price of the game will not be affected by the addition of content or updates, but is subject to market price updates.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121620/extras/889167285c6320c070a9ada4444cf141.avif?t=1736109859\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>The King Cat Clicker is an IDLE game where you click to earn coins and use the accumulated money to purchase upgrades that will help you earn more coins easily.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121620/extras/3e392d48d5636326231f36f01945d13c.poster.avif?t=1736109859\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121620/extras/3e392d48d5636326231f36f01945d13c.webm?t=1736109859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121620/extras/3e392d48d5636326231f36f01945d13c.mp4?t=1736109859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Real Cat Sounds<br></li><li> Upgrades Transform the World<br></li><li> Customization of Characters and the World<br></li><li> Replayability with Benefits<br></li><li> Cute Visuals</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121620/extras/889167285c6320c070a9ada4444cf141.avif?t=1736109859\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>The King Cat Clicker is an IDLE game where you click to earn coins and use the accumulated money to purchase upgrades that will help you earn more coins easily.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121620/extras/3e392d48d5636326231f36f01945d13c.poster.avif?t=1736109859\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121620/extras/3e392d48d5636326231f36f01945d13c.webm?t=1736109859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121620/extras/3e392d48d5636326231f36f01945d13c.mp4?t=1736109859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Real Cat Sounds<br></li><li> Upgrades Transform the World<br></li><li> Customization of Characters and the World<br></li><li> Replayability with Benefits<br></li><li> Cute Visuals</li></ul>",
